      "content": "Synthesis complete. The report has been written to `.planning/research/phases-21-22-deep-synthesis-2026-05-22.md`.\n\n---\n\n## RESEARCH COMPLETE\n\n**Phase:** 21-22 Synthesis\n**Confidence:** HIGH\n\n### Key Findings\n\n1. **Phase 21 (Session-Tracker):** 6 flaw categories fixed across 19 files, 8 gray-area decisions applied, 15/15 requirements verified. Temp leaks eliminated, manifest made derivative cache, childToRootMain now survives restart, anonymous children fixed, childCount populated, status preserved across callbacks, delegation always persisted.\n\n2. **Phase 21.1 (Execute-Slash-Command):** Complete rewrite from TUI-only to SDK-first with TUI fallback. Three dispatch paths: non-subtask (TUI), subtask (`session.prompt` + SubtaskPartInput), and synthetic parent prompt (`session.prompt` + text part). Two agent switching mechanisms. Original SDK-await design was disproved by live UAT — deferred scheduling is the corrected approach.\n\n3. **Phase 21.2 (Front-Agent Switching):** **SUPPORTED** at L1 runtime — OpenCode accepts subagent-mode agents for direct parent session prompts via the synthetic parent prompt path (`subtask:false + agent`). Prototype verified through live UAT after rebuild. No command or agent primitives were mutated.\n\n4. **Phase 22 (Status/Error Unification):** 9 requirements delivered. 12-code `DelegationErrorCode` const union, `DelegationError` struct, `delegationStatusToHarnessStatus()` mapping, notification retry (maxRetries=1 default) + TTL (5min default), `PendingNotificationRecord`/`PendingNotification` schema updates, `replayPending()` cleanup. All 3 quality gates passed (Lifecycle/Spec/Evidence).\n\n5. **Notification delivery chain:** Notifications are queued via `shouldQueuePending()` → `queuePending()` with retry/TTL gates, persisted via `persistAllPending()`, and delivered on `replayPending()` call. The actual `session.prompt()` to the parent session happens **outside** Phase 22 scope — in LifecycleManager/plugin.ts orchestration.\n\n6. **The notification design differs from \"append system message + reactivate stream\":** It uses passive pending notification replay with retry/TTL/idempotency, not active stream interruption.\n\n### File Created\n\n`.planning/research/phases-21-22-deep-synthesis-2026-05-22.md`\n\n### Ready for Planning\n\nResearch covers Phases 21, 21.1, 21.2, 22 in full depth — 70+ files consumed, all dispatch flows and notification chains documented with exact SDK method calls and signatures.",
